<h3>
  Action of parabolic subgroups on the Lie algebra of the unipotent radical
</h3>
<p>
  Share package since December 2001,
  communicated by Gerhard Hiss, Aachen.<br />
  This package has not yet been transferred to or replaced in
  <mixer var="GAP4"/>. You can use it only in <mixer var="GAP3"/>.
</p>

<h3>
  Authors
</h3>
<p>
