  <mixer person="Gerhard Erich Roehrle" data="name"/>.
</p>

<h3>
  Implementation
</h3>
<p>
  <b>Language:</b> <mixer var="GAP3"/> <br />
  <b>Operating system:</b> Any <br />
  <b>Current version:</b> 1.0 (in the 3.4.4 distribution)
</p>

<h3>
  Description
</h3>
<p>
  MOP is designed to compute upper bounds for the modality of the action
  of parabolic subgroups P on p<sub>u</sub>, the Lie algebra of the
  unipotent radical of P, for simple algebraic groups G over an
  algebraically closed field K. It is a <mixer var="GAP3"/> share package
  based on the CHEVIE package.
</p>

